{
  "stem": "7739.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was the [NON-ENGLISH], and there was the [NON-ENGLISH], and there was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So some people worked on the [NON-ENGLISH], which was planing mill.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were making wood products, mainly ammunition boxes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we worked in the ammunition factories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were making, out of iron ore and scrap metal-- we were making steel for ammunition.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were accommodated in these three camps and you had to get used to do life in the camp, of course.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "As soon as I got to the camp-- no, before we got to the camp, we were assembled in a place called [NON-ENGLISH], which means a rifle range.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There were two banks of earth on both sides, and on the front was the rifle range.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the fellow by the name of-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I forget his name, it'll come back to me-- made a speech, an SS man.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I guess he was an SS man, or a state man in black uniform, that we should surrender all valuables-- money, watches, jewelery, foreign currencies, whatever we had of value to.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there was a huge box there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he made the people go through and throw everything that was of value there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "As soon as about 20 people went by, he stopped about three or four people and he searched them to see, make sure that everything was put in.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And if he found anything on somebody, he made them wait there and another few people went by and he stopped another few people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Then he stopped about five or eight people who didn't throw everything in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He ordered two or three soldiers to come.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He'd put them up against the wall and shot them right in front of everybody there.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
